All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    This class holds test data created to try the software with ease.
    DataMenu
    This class shows a menu with the objective of write and delete matches in a human readable way.
    Exceptions
    This class holds all methods related about let the user know of undesirable use of the user input methods.
    Input
    This class holds all methods related to the modification of user input in order to produce a specific product.
    Main
    This is the core of the execution, it runs the main menu and executes it again if the input is not zero.
    MainMenu
    This set of procedures eases link between all the possible menus that the application has.
    Match
    Object Match contains two teams and the time it lasted in minutes.
    MatchesMenu
    This class shows the menu that enables screen printing of the existent matches, teams and teammates in an human readable way.
    ScoreMenu  
    Season
    Object Season contains all the matches registered.
    Statistics
    Object Stadistics holds all the data related to a teammate on a specified match.
    Team
    Object Team, stores five Teammates that will form part of a Match.
    Teammate
    Object Teammate, stores data related to its identification String and a vector of String that are its in-game items.
    TeamRandomizer
    This class has a tool to create random teams.
    Utils
    This class holds miscellaneous methods related to work with data.
